Interface Input

All Known Subinterfaces:
CommandInput, OptionInput, ParameterInput
All Known Implementing Classes:
CommandInputImpl, OptionInputImpl, ParameterInputImpl
public interface Input

Input interface is the common interface of all command line inputs. Command line parameters, options and command keywords are all possible inputs.
